Coin Info

Exchange Rate
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/exchangerate/current

Single Address Info
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/address/info/[address]

Multiple Address Info
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/address/info/[address1],[address2]

Single Address Balance
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/address/balance/[address]

Multiple Address Balance
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/address/balance/[address1],[address2]

Block Info
http://btc.blockr.io/api/v1/block/info/[parameter]
Where parameter can be:
- block number (eg: 223212)
- block hash (eg: 0000000000000000210b10d620600dc1cc2380bb58eb2408f9767eb792ed31fa)
- word "last" - this will always return the latest block
- word "first" - this will always return the first block